<% provide(:title,'About') %>
<div class="container">
	<div class="aboutTop">
		<div class="aboutBg">
		</div>
		<div class="authorImg">
			<%= image_tag('pic.jpeg') %>
		</div>
		<div class="authorData">
			<h2><strong><%= current_admin.name %></strong> <span>Web前端开发者 <a class="introduceChange"><span class="fa fa-edit fa-fw"></span></a></span></h2>
			<p>世界那么大,总归得撒开步子到处去望望,看看那妖娆迷人的世界。</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="aboutContent">
		<div class="authorException">
			<div>
				<h3>作者简介<span>(brief introduction)</span></h3>
				<p><%= @about.try(:introduce) %></p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3>作者技术知识介绍<span>(Knowledge introduction)</span></h3>
				<%= @about.try(:knowledge).html_safe %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="authorBasicData">
			<div>
				<h3>作者职业经历<span>(work experience)</span></h3>
				<%= @about.try(:exception).html_safe %>
			</div>
			<div class="contact">
				<h3>作者联系方式<span>(Contact information)</span></h3>
				<%= @about.try(:contact).html_safe %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="aboutWeb">
			<div>
				<h3>关于网站<span>(about website)</span></h3>
				<p>此个人网站于2018年正式上线,作用于个人文章、信息的发布,站内信息允许转载,若未经允许运用于商业用途将视情况提起诉讼。对于站内部分转载的内容,如涉及版权问题,请及时联系作者进行更改、删除。作者保留对网站的所有解释权。</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<%= render 'generalPurpose/about_edit' %>